subdefinitions.definition: A sudden , sharp blow , knock , or slap ; a rap , a whack .
The sound made by such a blow, knock, or slap.
( agriculture ) Synonym of chattering damsel ( “ a component of a traditional mill which creates a vibratory motion to impel portions of grain toward the millstone ; a clapper ” ) .

definitions.definition: ( figurative , gambling , chiefly dice games , obsolete ) A method of cheating at a dice game .

definitions.definition: A piece of raised ground or a short , steep slope ; a small hill ; a hillock , a knoll .
The crest or top of a hill.
